Package nusri.fyp.demo.roboflow.data.request

Class Sam2SegmentationRequest

java.lang.Object
nusri.fyp.demo.roboflow.data.RoboflowRequestData
nusri.fyp.demo.roboflow.data.request.Sam2SegmentationRequest
public class Sam2SegmentationRequest extends RoboflowRequestData
Represents a request to perform segmentation using the SAM2 (Segment Anything Model) model.
This request is used to send an image for segmentation using the SAM2 model. The request can include prompts, configuration options for image format, and cache settings, among other parameters.
